high_descs: Move forward to the toilet paper holder
Pick up the toilet paper on the holder.
Turn around and walk forward until you reach the empty shelf, then turn right.
Place the toilet paper on the empty shelf.
anns.task_desc: Move the toilet paper to the shelf.

high_descs: Walk forward to the wall left of the toilet
Pick up the toilet paper roll from the toilet paper roll holder
Turn around and walk to the first white shelf
Put the toilet paper on the shelf
anns.task_desc: Put the toilet paper on the white shelf

high_descs: Walk to the toilet paper holder that is on the wall to the left of the toilet.
Remove the roll of toilet paper.
Turn around to the left and walk to the white cabinet that is closest to the toilet.
Place the roll of toilet paper on top of the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Move a roll of toilet paper from a holder to the top of a cabinet.
